      <title>Kilmar Abrego Garcia detained by ICE during Baltimore check-in</title>
      <author>Sergio Martínez-Beltrán</author>
      <link>https://www.npr.org/2025/08/25/nx-s1-5515422/kilmar-abrego-garcia-detained-ice</link>
